### Variables
@baseUrl = https://YOUR_PROJECT_REF.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Créer événement complet (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "mariage",
  "event_category": "cérémonie",
  "title": "Mariage de Jean et Marie",
  "event_date": "2024-12-25T18:00:00Z",
  "venue_id": "venue-uuid-here",
  "guest_count": 150,
  "budget_min": 5000000,
  "budget_max": 10000000,
  "style": "moderne",
  "is_hybrid": false
}

### Test 2 - Créer événement minimal (sans lieu)
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "séminaire",
  "title": "Séminaire Entreprise",
  "event_date": "2024-11-15T09:00:00Z",
  "guest_count": 50
}

### Test 3 - Erreur: date dans le passé
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "concert",
  "title": "Concert",
  "event_date": "2020-01-01T18:00:00Z"
}

### Test 4 - Erreur: titre manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "mariage",
  "event_date": "2024-12-25T18:00:00Z"
}

### Test 5 - Erreur: capacité dépassée
POST {{baseUrl}}/events/create-event
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_type": "mariage",
  "title": "Grand Mariage",
  "event_date": "2024-12-25T18:00:00Z",
  "venue_id": "venue-uuid-here",
  "guest_count": 1000
}

